SUB_W11_EVAR_BOFO_LOVE_100_CUT_000_070.text:
Worry not, Lela. Merely plant the seeds.
You are chosen by the god of the Imeru;
the markings on your face serve as proof.

SUB_W11_EVAR_BOFO_TABLET_120_CUT_000_010.text:
So what is this tablet even made of?
It's not stone or wood, that's for sure;
in fact, I've never felt anything like it.

SUB_W11_GIMK_BOFO_POLLEN_120_CUT_000_030.text:
I mean, I suppose it's not impossible;
this world does have fiends, after all.
But I guess we'll never know.

SUB_W11_EVAR_BOFO_AREAIN_300_CUT_000_141.text:
Sure would be nice if we got a say in this;
I'm fed up of just having responsibility
dumped on our heads.

SUB_W11_EVAR_BOFO_STRENGTH_320_CUT_010_0.text:
That must have made Hasumi feel awful;
I'm sure she regretted not being able to
guide Nuy through her trials to the end.
